{"tid":2243396,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撐政府男生遭廿名同學聯手襲擊 再多一名15歲男童認罪","createTime":"2020-10-14T16:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T09:35:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3bed13d170dfe525ee883c6e40750dd516c4c84a","tid":2243396,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T16:48:49.000Z","msg":"就讀筲箕灣某中學的15歲男生去年疑因撐政府，在校內遭20名同學掟水樽等物件襲擊，遇襲男生事後向教師及父母揭發事件，報警求助，結果三男兩女同學被拘控普通襲擊罪。早前一人認罪後，其餘四名學生今在東區法院少年法庭再提訊，當中再多一名男生認罪，裁判官黃雅茵為他索閱報告，下月10日判刑，其餘三人明年2月17日受審。各被告繼續保釋。<br />\n<br />\n四名少年被告年齡介乎14至15歲，分別是兩男兩女，他們同被控一項普通襲擊罪，今日認罪的是其中一名15歲男生。裁判官今就該男生認罪，宣佈控罪得以證實（charge proved），並押後為他索取感化官及社會服務令報告才判刑。據了解，有關程序一般被視為被告有機會免留案底的出路，裁判官或因報告內容正面，考慮判以保護令而不留案底。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/PGYFMG3TNVHAHDA2VPGUKWHAM4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2FPGYFMG3TNVHAHDA2VPGUKWHAM4%2F&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiaha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=9c3d3584\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201014%2FPGYFMG3TNVHAHDA2VPGUKWHAM4%2F&h=06595698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201014/PGYFMG3TNVHAHDA2VPGUKWHAM4/</a>"},{"pid":"995d23f9a7e2d61c6a4677463c51990edd236bb7","tid":2243396,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4f79c703cf14b0b527951661cffd15fd97d25d","tid":2243396,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"995d23f9a7e2d61c6a4677463c51990edd236bb7","tid":2243396,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\"